title: Viral Hit
synopsis: Scrawny high school student Hobin Yu is probably the last guy youâ€™d expect to star in a NewTube channel that revolves around fighting. But after following some advice from a mysterious NewTube channel, Hobin is soon knocking out guys stronger than him and raking in more money than he could have ever dreamed of. Can Hobin keep this up, or will he eventually meet his match?
author: TaejunPak,KimJunghyun
